## 13. Minimal CogOS Implementation (MVP)

A system qualifies as CogOS if it implements:

1. ThoughtObjects (logged decisions)
2. StateVector (persistent identity)
3. Invariants (ethical + logical constraints)
4. Decision Gate (Œ£C)
5. Ledger (memory with lineage)
6. Distillation (pattern extraction)

Everything else is optional but amplifying.

